  "readme": "# UI Skills\n\n![UI Skills](./public/UI-OG.webp)\n\nSkills for Design Engineers\n\nMore on [ui-skills.com](http://ui-skills.com/)\n\nRun `npx ui-skills start` to route your agent through the right UI skill set for the task.\n\n## CLI\n\n```bash\nnpx ui-skills\nnpx ui-skills start\nnpx ui-skills categories\nnpx ui-skills list --category motion\nnpx ui-skills get baseline-ui\n```\n\n## License\n\nLicensed under the [MIT license](https://github.com/ibelick/ui-skills/blob/main/LICENSE).\n",
  "readmeHtml": "<h1>UI Skills</h1>\n<p>![UI Skills](./public/UI-OG.webp)</p>\n<p>Skills for Design Engineers</p>\n<p>More on <a href=\"http://ui-skills.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ui-skills.com</a></p>\n<p>Run <code>npx ui-skills start</code> to route your agent through the right UI skill set for the task.</p>\n<h2>CLI</h2>\n<pre><code>\nnpx ui-skills\n\nnpx ui-skills start\n\nnpx ui-skills categories\n\nnpx ui-skills list --category motion\n\nnpx ui-skills get baseline-ui\n\n</code></pre>\n<h2>License</h2>\n<p>Licensed under the <a href=\"https://github.com/ibelick/ui-skills/blob/main/LICENSE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">MIT license</a>.</p>",
